{\up +}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up +} BROWSE0027:0067}
{\up $}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up $} What is Help Workshop?}
{\up #}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up #} BAS_THE_HELP_COMPILER}
\pard\sb115\sa35\sl-235\li115\ri125 {\up A}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up A} BAS_HCW;BAS_THE_HELP_COMPILER}
{\up K}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up K} executable name for Help Workshop;filename for Help Workshop;Help Workshop;Help Workshop, about Help Workshop;what is Help Workshop? Hcw.exe}
\f1\b\fs16 What is Help Workshop?
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 Help Workshop is a program that you use to create Help (.hlp) files, edit project and contents files, and test and report on help files. Help Workshop takes the information in the project (.hpj) file to combine the topic (.rtf) files, bitmaps, and other sources into one Help file that can be viewed using the Microsoft Windows Help program.
\par Help Workshop\plain\f0\fs16 \'92\f1 s executable name is hcw.exe.
\par \pard\sl-115\li265\ri125\fi-185\brdrb\brdrs\tx295 
\par \pard\sb45\sl-235\li295\ri125\fi-185\tx295 \{button ,AL(`BAS_COMPILE_MSG;HCW;HCRTF;TMPDIR')\} \uldb Related Topics\plain\f1\fs16 {\v %!AL(`BAS_COMPILE_MSG;HCW;HCRTF;TMPDIR')}
\par \page
{\up +}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up +} BROWSE0027:0068}
{\up $}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up $} Help Workshop components}
{\up #}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up #} SDK_FILES_DOCS}
\pard\sb115\sa35\sl-235\li115\ri125 {\up A}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up A} getstart;SDK_FILES_DOCS}
{\up K}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up K} bitmaps;bitmaps, about Multi-Resolution Bitmap Compiler;components of Help Workshop;files;files, components of Help Workshop;Hcrtf.exe;Hcw.exe;Hcw.hlp;Help Author's Guide;Help Workshop;Help Workshop, about Help Workshop;Hotspot Editor;Hotspot Editor, about Hotspot Editor;Mrbc.exe;multi-resolution graphics;multi-resolution graphics, compiler (mrbc.exe);Shed.exe}
\b Help Workshop components
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 Help Workshop includes the following files and documents:
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li295\ri125\fi-185\tx295 \f2 \'b7\f1 \tab Help Workshop (Hcw.exe and Hcrtf.exe).  Enables you to edit project and contents files, and to compile, test, and create reports for Help files.
\par \pard\sb45\sl-235\li295\ri125\fi-185\tx295 \f2 \'b7\f1 \tab Help Author's Guide (Hcw.hlp).  Describes how to author and compile Help files by using Help Workshop.
\par \f2 \'b7\f1 \tab Hotspot Editor version 2.0 (Shed.exe).  Enables you to create a graphic that has multiple \ul hotspots.\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 7BM6.K}
\par \f2 \'b7\f1 \tab Multi-Resolution Bitmap Compiler version 1.1 (Mrbc.exe).  Enables you to create bitmaps that have different resolutions. You can combine these bitmaps into a single graphic to compensate for differences between the aspect ratios of the bitmaps and the aspect ratio supported by a user's display.
\par \pard\sl-115\li265\ri125\fi-185\brdrb\brdrs\tx295 
\par \pard\sb45\sl-235\li295\ri125\fi-185\tx295 \{button ,AL(`BAS_MULT_RESOLUTION;BAS_THE_HELP_COMPILER;MRBC;SHED')\} \uldb Related Topics\plain\f1\fs16 {\v %!AL(`BAS_MULT_RESOLUTION;BAS_THE_HELP_COMPILER;MRBC;SHED')}
\par \page
