\par \pard\keepn\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \fs16 BackFlush()\plain\f1\fs16 
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 Removes the back history list from the current window. This macro does not affect the history list displayed in the History window.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125 \b Parameters
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 This macro does not take any parameters.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125 \b Comment
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 Help Workshop automatically converts the BackFlush macro to BF, which is the only form of this macro that WinHelp can use.
