\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 Help Workshop automatically converts the ChangeItemBinding macro to CIB.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 \b Example
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 \plain\f1\fs16 The following macro changes the menu item identified by "notepad_item" to open the Notepad program:
\par \pard\sb45\sl-235\li295\ri125\fi-185\tx295 \tab ChangeItemBinding(notepad_item, ExecFile(notepad))
