\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li1575\ri125\fi-1455\tx1575 item-ID\tab Identifies a menu item that was previously appended by the AppendItem, ExtInsertItem, or InsertItem macro.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 \b Comments
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 \plain\f1\fs16 The menu item cannot be used in the topic until the EnableItem or ExtAbleItem macro is run.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 WinHelp ignores this macro if it is run in a secondary window.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1575 Help Workshop automatically converts the DisableItem macro to DI.
