\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li1435\ri125\fi-1305\tx1435\tx1575 keyword\tab Specifies one or more A-keywords to search for. Separate multiple keywords using semicolons. If a keyword contains a comma, enclose the entire keyword string in quotation marks.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1435\tx1575 \b Comment
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1435\tx1575 \plain\f1\fs16 If an effective link is found, TestALink returns a value of "1".
