\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 Removes from a menu item the check mark that was placed by the CheckItem macro.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li1435\ri125\fi-1305\brdrb\brdrs\tx1435 \b Parameter\tab Description\plain\f1\fs16 
\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li1435\ri125\fi-1305\tx1435 item-ID\tab Identifies the menu item to uncheck. The ID must have been created by the AppendItem or InsertItem macros, or must be a standard WinHelp menu item ID.
