\b\fs24 COPYRIGHT
\par \pard\keepn\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \fs16 COPYRIGHT=\plain\f1\fs16 copyright-notice
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 You specify the COPYRIGHT option in the [OPTIONS] section of the project (.hpj) file. COPYRIGHT places a custom copyright notice in the Version dialog box of WinHelp. WinHelp displays the notice immediately below the Microsoft copyright notice. You can specify up to 255 characters (127 for DBCS languages) as the copyright text.
