\b\fs24 DEFFONT
\par \pard\keepn\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \fs16 DEFFONT=\plain\f1\fs16 fontname, font-size, charset
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 You specify the DEFFONT option in the [OPTIONS] section of the project (.hpj) file. DEFFONT specifies the default font for the lists on the Contents, Index and Find tabs and in the Topics Found dialog box.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li1625\ri125\fi-1495\brdrb\brdrs\tx1615 \b Parameter\tab Description\plain\f1\fs16 
\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li1625\ri125\fi-1495\tx1615 fontname\tab Specifies the name of the font to use.
\par font-size\tab Specifies the point size of the font to use.
\par charset\tab Specifies the character set (CHARSET) to use.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1615 \b Comment
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1615 \plain\f1\fs16 The DEFFONT option is new.
