\par base\tab Byte offset to the beginning of a display text region to query.
\par limit\tab Byte offset to just beyond the end of a display text reqion. You may use -1 to indicate the end of the entire display text.
\par paHilites\tab Address of a vector of \b HILITE\plain\f1\fs16  items. The hilite results will be copied to this vector. It is presumed to be large enough to contain all the hilites for the region. You can find out how many hilites will be returned by calling \b CountHiltes\plain\f1\fs16  first.
