\par pbImages\tab Address of the buffer containing the phrase images.
\par cbImages\tab Count of phrase images.
\par pacbImageCompressed\tab Address of the buffer containing information about the phrase sizes.
\par cbCompressed\tab Size in bytes of the compressed image data.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1975 \b Return Value
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125\tx1975 \plain\f1\fs16 Returns 0 if successful; an error value otherwise.
\par \pard\sl-115\li265\ri125\fi-185\brdrb\brdrs\tx295 
