\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li1885\ri125\fi-1755\tx1885 pWordToStem\tab Address of the null-terminated word string which is to be stemmed. The string is a Unicode string where each character is represented by a 16-bit value, and the terminating null is a 16-bit zero.
