\b\fs24 WinHelp-specific Project File Options
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 These options are supported by Help Workshop but not the Viewer compiler. Use Help Workshop to add or edit these options.
\par \pard\sb115\sl-235\li1985\ri125\fi-1855\brdrb\brdrs\tx425\tx575\tx1975 \b Option\tab Description
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li1985\ri125\fi-1855\tx1975 \uldb \plain\f1\uldb\fs16 CHARSET\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 0H87TF}\tab Specifies the character set to use for all fonts.
\par \uldb CNT\plain\f1\fs16 {\v RB3WX}\tab Specifies the name of the \ul contents (.CNT) file.\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 2GB40S} to associate with the Help (.HLP) file.
\par \uldb DBCS\plain\f1\fs16 {\v RB4KGS}\tab Specifies that the topic (.RTF) files use a double-byte character set
\par \uldb DEFFONT\plain\f1\fs16 {\v ECK4F6}\tab Specifies the default font to use in WinHelp.
\par \uldb ERRORLOG\plain\f1\fs16 {\v YCLLJE}\tab Specifies the name of the log file to create when compiling the Help file.
\par \uldb FORCEFONT\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 24ML4CE}\tab Forces WinHelp to use the specified font when displaying the Help file, in place of the fonts used in the topic files.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li1985\ri125\fi-1855\tx1975 \uldb FTS\plain\f1\fs16 {\v RB72W}\tab Specifies the level of information to include in the full-text search index file.
\par \uldb HCW\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 2OLG6TE}\tab Reserved for use by Help Workshop.
\par \uldb HLP\plain\f1\fs16 {\v RB8UT}\tab Specifies the name of the Help file to create.
\par \uldb INDEX_SEPARATORS\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 2A9VNJZ}\tab Identifies the characters used to denote separate keyword entries in topics.
\par \uldb LCID\plain\f1\fs16 {\v RB.LMD}\tab Specifies the locale ID.
\par \uldb MAPFONTSIZE\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 12DOBQV}\tab Maps font sizes specified in the topic files to different sizes when displayed in the WinHelp window.
\par \uldb MULTIKEY\plain\f1\fs16 {\v K.Z2KQ}\tab Customizes the keyword search so that it uses more than one keyword table.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li1985\ri125\fi-1855\tx1975 \uldb NOTES\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 15Q.CUI}\tab Specifies whether or not the compiler will display any notes during compilation.
\par \uldb OLDKEYPHRASE\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 4_QY9B}\tab Specifies whether or not to create a new keyword phrase (.PH) file.
\par \uldb REPLACE\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 06VZSZ}\tab Specifies a path prefix to replace and its replacement.
\par \uldb REPORT\plain\f1\fs16 {\v JOHTZB}\tab Specifies whether or not to display messages when compiling the Help file.
\par \uldb TMPDIR\plain\f1\fs16 {\v 2NHAHAE}\tab Specifies the folder to place the temporary files created while compiling the Help file.
\par \pard\sl-115\li265\ri125\fi-185\brdrb\brdrs\tx295 
