\b Help system limits
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs16 The 32-bit technology of Windows\'a095 enables WinHelp version 4.0 to dramatically expand the capability of the Help system you author. 
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li2515\ri125\fi-2385\brdrb\brdrs\tx2515 \b Item\tab Limit\plain\f1\fs16 
